            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EJohn%20designates%20three%20types%20of%20Christians%2C%20according%20to%20their%20maturity%20levels.%20His%20first%20exhortation%20is%20to%20the%20%22dear%20children%22%20whose%20entire%20experience%20and%20excitement%20revolves%20around%20the%20knowledge%20that%20their%20sins%20have%20been%20forgiven.%20Every%20new%20Christian%20needs%20to%20be%20taught%20and%20discipled%20in%20this%20simple%20truth.%20Unfortunately%2C%20most%20believers%20never%20fully%20enjoy%20the%20one%20basic%20fact%20that%20their%20sins%20have%20been%20forgiven%20on%20account%20of%20Jesus.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20second%20level%20of%20Christian%20maturity%20is%20the%20%22young%22%20(1%20John%202%3A13).%20These%20Christians%20have%20moved%20into%20the%20level%20of%20spiritual%20warfare.%20They%20are%20strong%20in%20God's%20Word%20and%20have%20overcome%20the%20devil%20(v.%2014).%20They%20have%20allowed%20God%20to%20tear%20down%20the%20strongholds%20of%20Satan%20over%20their%20minds%2C%20bodies%2C%20and%20past%20struggles.%20They%20understand%20the%20truths%20of%20spiritual%20freedom%20from%20bondage%20and%20live%20in%20that%20freedom.%20%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20last%20group%20is%20the%20%22mature%2C%22%20who%20know%20Christ%20(v.%2013).%20These%20people%2C%20walking%20in%20close%20relationship%20with%20God%2C%20know%20Him%20as%20more%20than%20just%20Forgiver%20and%20Deliverer.%20They%20know%20God%20as%20Father%20in%20spiritual%20worship%20and%20intimacy.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EGrow%20up%2C%20little%20one.%20Your%20Father%20has%20more%20of%20His%20goodness%20for%20you%20to%20enjoy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Daniel.8:1-27",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EDaniel%208%3A1-27%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_1%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EDaniel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EDaniel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Vision%20of%20a%20Ram%20and%20Goat%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20original%20text%20from%20this%20point%20through%20chapter%26%23xA0%3B12%20is%20in%20Hebrew.%20See%20note%20at%202%3A4.%3C%2Fspan%3EDuring%20the%20third%20year%20of%20King%20Belshazzar%26%23x2019%3Bs%20reign%2C%20I%2C%20Daniel%2C%20saw%20another%20vision%2C%20following%20the%20one%20that%20had%20already%20appeared%20to%20me.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_2%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20this%20vision%20I%20was%20at%20the%20fortress%20of%20Susa%2C%20in%20the%20province%20of%20Elam%2C%20standing%20beside%20the%20Ulai%20River.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20Ulai%20Gate%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%208%3A16.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_3%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20I%20looked%20up%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20ram%20with%20two%20long%20horns%20standing%20beside%20the%20river.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20gate%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%208%3A6.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20One%20of%20the%20horns%20was%20longer%20than%20the%20other%2C%20even%20though%20it%20had%20grown%20later%20than%20the%20other%20one.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_4%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20ram%20butted%20everything%20out%20of%20his%20way%20to%20the%20west%2C%20to%20the%20north%2C%20and%20to%20the%20south%2C%20and%20no%20one%20could%20stand%20against%20him%20or%20help%20his%20victims.%20He%20did%20as%20he%20pleased%20and%20became%20very%20great.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_5%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EWhile%20I%20was%20watching%2C%20suddenly%20a%20male%20goat%20appeared%20from%20the%20west%2C%20crossing%20the%20land%20so%20swiftly%20that%20he%20didn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20even%20touch%20the%20ground.%20This%20goat%2C%20which%20had%20one%20very%20large%20horn%20between%20its%20eyes%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_6%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3Eheaded%20toward%20the%20two-horned%20ram%20that%20I%20had%20seen%20standing%20beside%20the%20river%2C%20rushing%20at%20him%20in%20a%20rage.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_7%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20goat%20charged%20furiously%20at%20the%20ram%20and%20struck%20him%2C%20breaking%20off%20both%20his%20horns.%20Now%20the%20ram%20was%20helpless%2C%20and%20the%20goat%20knocked%20him%20down%20and%20trampled%20him.%20No%20one%20could%20rescue%20the%20ram%20from%20the%20goat%26%23x2019%3Bs%20power.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_8%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20goat%20became%20very%20powerful.%20But%20at%20the%20height%20of%20his%20power%2C%20his%20large%20horn%20was%20broken%20off.%20In%20the%20large%20horn%26%23x2019%3Bs%20place%20grew%20four%20prominent%20horns%20pointing%20in%20the%20four%20directions%20of%20the%20earth.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_9%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20from%20one%20of%20the%20prominent%20horns%20came%20a%20small%20horn%20whose%20power%20grew%20very%20great.%20It%20extended%20toward%20the%20south%20and%20the%20east%20and%20toward%20the%20glorious%20land%20of%20Israel.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_10%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EIts%20power%20reached%20to%20the%20heavens%2C%20where%20it%20attacked%20the%20heavenly%20army%2C%20throwing%20some%20of%20the%20heavenly%20beings%20and%20some%20of%20the%20stars%20to%20the%20ground%20and%20trampling%20them.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_11%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20even%20challenged%20the%20Commander%20of%20heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20army%20by%20canceling%20the%20daily%20sacrifices%20offered%20to%20him%20and%20by%20destroying%20his%20Temple.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_12%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20army%20of%20heaven%20was%20restrained%20from%20responding%20to%20this%20rebellion.%20So%20the%20daily%20sacrifice%20was%20halted%2C%20and%20truth%20was%20overthrown.%20The%20horn%20succeeded%20in%20everything%20it%20did.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A11-12%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20meaning%20of%20the%20Hebrew%20for%20these%20verses%20is%20uncertain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_13%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20I%20heard%20two%20holy%20ones%20talking%20to%20each%20other.%20One%20of%20them%20asked%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BHow%20long%20will%20the%20events%20of%20this%20vision%20last%3F%20How%20long%20will%20the%20rebellion%20that%20causes%20desecration%20stop%20the%20daily%20sacrifices%3F%20How%20long%20will%20the%20Temple%20and%20heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20army%20be%20trampled%20on%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_14%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20other%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BIt%20will%20take%202%2C300%20evenings%20and%20mornings%3B%20then%20the%20Temple%20will%20be%20made%20right%20again.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_15%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EGabriel%20Explains%20the%20Vision%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20I%2C%20Daniel%2C%20was%20trying%20to%20understand%20the%20meaning%20of%20this%20vision%2C%20someone%20who%20looked%20like%20a%20man%20stood%20in%20front%20of%20me.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_16%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20I%20heard%20a%20human%20voice%20calling%20out%20from%20the%20Ulai%20River%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BGabriel%2C%20tell%20this%20man%20the%20meaning%20of%20his%20vision.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_17%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EAs%20Gabriel%20approached%20the%20place%20where%20I%20was%20standing%2C%20I%20became%20so%20terrified%20that%20I%20fell%20with%20my%20face%20to%20the%20ground.%20%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Byou%20must%20understand%20that%20the%20events%20you%20have%20seen%20in%20your%20vision%20relate%20to%20the%20time%20of%20the%20end.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_18%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EWhile%20he%20was%20speaking%2C%20I%20fainted%20and%20lay%20there%20with%20my%20face%20to%20the%20ground.%20But%20Gabriel%20roused%20me%20with%20a%20touch%20and%20helped%20me%20to%20my%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_19%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20am%20here%20to%20tell%20you%20what%20will%20happen%20later%20in%20the%20time%20of%20wrath.%20What%20you%20have%20seen%20pertains%20to%20the%20very%20end%20of%20time.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_20%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20two-horned%20ram%20represents%20the%20kings%20of%20Media%20and%20Persia.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_21%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20shaggy%20male%20goat%20represents%20the%20king%20of%20Greece%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A21%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eof%20Javan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20the%20large%20horn%20between%20his%20eyes%20represents%20the%20first%20king%20of%20the%20Greek%20Empire.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_22%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20four%20prominent%20horns%20that%20replaced%20the%20one%20large%20horn%20show%20that%20the%20Greek%20Empire%20will%20break%20into%20four%20kingdoms%2C%20but%20none%20as%20great%20as%20the%20first.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_23%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20their%20rule%2C%20when%20their%20sin%20is%20at%20its%20height%2C%20a%20fierce%20king%2C%20a%20master%20of%20intrigue%2C%20will%20rise%20to%20power.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_24%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20will%20become%20very%20strong%2C%20but%20not%20by%20his%20own%20power.%20He%20will%20cause%20a%20shocking%20amount%20of%20destruction%20and%20succeed%20in%20everything%20he%20does.%20He%20will%20destroy%20powerful%20leaders%20and%20devastate%20the%20holy%20people.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_25%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20will%20be%20a%20master%20of%20deception%20and%20will%20become%20arrogant%3B%20he%20will%20destroy%20many%20without%20warning.%20He%20will%20even%20take%20on%20the%20Prince%20of%20princes%20in%20battle%2C%20but%20he%20will%20be%20broken%2C%20though%20not%20by%20human%20power.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22dani_8_26%22%20bk%3D%22dani%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20vision%20about%20the%202%2C300%20evenings%20and%20mornings%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20